  <b>Directory Sync</b>
  <p>Due to my previous work at Netlify with team management and user authentication, I was given the task of writing docs for our new Directory Sync feature. Directory Sync allowed Netlify organizations to manage user access across multiple teams using a supported identity provider. I worked closely with the engineers on the project to set up my own organization with users and test the functionality. I also worked alongside the designers to test the in-app flow, and I made suggestions to improve the overall usability and experience.</p>
